        {
            "title": "津上機床中國發盈喜 料首季盈利增約40%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">津上機床中國(01651)發盈喜，預期今年首季公司擁有人應佔溢利約10.94億元(人民幣‧下同)，較去年同期的7.82億元增約40%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"津上機床中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/01651-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"津上機床中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/01651-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">津上機床中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會認為，首季盈利提升主要受惠於中國經濟形勢持續向好、國內製造業的設備需求繼續增長的良好態勢，包括汽車行業、3C行業及氣動液壓行業的資本開支均在增長。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司又指出，AI液冷、半導體等新興領域的快速發展，對高精度、自動化、復合化機床設備的需求持續提升，也成為該公司業績增長的主要驅動力，再加上公司推進全員參與的降本增效改善活動取得顯著成效，盈利水平得到明顯提升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會認為，機床行業的表現具有週期性起伏變化，上述財務業績的變化幅度在公司的預料範圍之內。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15899334-%e6%b4%a5%e4%b8%8a%e6%a9%9f%e5%ba%8a%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%99%bc%e7%9b%88%e5%96%9c-%e6%96%99%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%a2%9e%e7%b4%8440",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/01651.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 12:20:05",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱窄幅爭持 恒指半日升33點報26394點 寧德時代破頂成藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">正當日韓台等地股市破頂或升近歷史高位之際，港股今早卻只能窄幅波動，寧德時代(03750)在創新高的同時也成表現最佳藍籌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早高開81點後曾於初段衝上26486點半日高位，將升幅擴大至125點，其後便陷入窄幅爭持局面，最低曾見26342點，倒跌19點，半日波幅僅144點；恒指中午收報26394點，升33點或0.13%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174835__source-web_00941-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174835__source-web_00941-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：寧德時代官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250508_FI_source-web_CATL-4-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：寧德時代官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174835__source-web_00941-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數明顯跑輸大市，開市不足10分鐘已開始倒跌，半日跌37點或0.74%，報5028點；國企指數升7點或0.09%，報8906點。主板半日成交1087.89億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日升19點，報26409點，高水14點。科指期貨跌37點，報5033點，高水5點。國指期貨升2點，報8910點，高水3點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股11.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅科股是拖大市後腿的主力，「ATMXJ」全線報跌，阿里巴巴(09988)跌1.24%，報135.3元；騰訊(00700)跌0.96%，報517.5元。單是這兩大重磅科股，合共已拖低恒指逾46點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">「ATMXJ」其餘3位成員方面，美團(03690)跌0.47%，報84.75元；京東(09618)跌0.33%，報122元；小米(01810)亦跌0.37%，報32.2元。舜宇光學(02382)則在藍籌中表現包尾，跌3.47%，報63.95元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地車股同樣受壓，比亞迪(01211)跌1.09%，報108.8元；吉利汽車(00175)跌1.33%，報23.78元；理想汽車(02015)跌1.3%，報72.35元。蔚來(09866)跌1.22%，報52.6元；小鵬汽車(09868)更挫2.09%，報67.95元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-web_01211-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">之前曾受配股傳聞與小股東就減持A股詢價消息影響的寧德時代，在持股6.23%的寧波聯合創新完成減持詢價後，今早A、H齊回升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代A股(300750.SZ)半日升1.94%，報440.89元人民幣。該公司H股更創歷史新高，最高見745元；中午收報741.5元，仍漲5.55%，單是H股市值已膨脹至1156.15億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">多隻傳統藍籌重磅股則聯手擔起撐市重任，中國移動(00941)派首季成績表後，股價今早全程報升，中午收報83.15元，升1.65%，創3個月高位。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174835__source-web_00941-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230703-174835__source-web_00941-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國移動官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藍籌內銀均造好，工商銀行(01398)、建設銀行(00939)、中國銀行(03988)齊創逾3年高位，建行升1.01%，報8.97元；工行升0.97%，報7.26元；中行也升0.58%，報5.24元。招商銀行(03968)則升0.69%，報51.45元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">兩大藍籌國際金融股則個別發展，滙控(00005)升0.49%，報142.9元；友邦(01299)則跌0.24%，報83.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，暫是今年香港IPO集資額最多的勝宏科技(02476)，股份今早登場，一直穩企招股價之上，低位302元亦較招股價209.88元高43.89%；中午收報315元，高於招股價50.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">齊於上周五掛牌的兩隻半新股，今日齊再創新高兼躋身主板成交額20大榜上，其中群核科技(00068)經過首兩日急升後，今早略為反覆，中段曾倒跌最多13.78%，中午收報40.96元，升9.4%。長光辰芯(03277)更飆21.93%，報87.3元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15899308-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e7%88%ad%e6%8c%81-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%8733%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126394%e9%bb%9e-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-8.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 12:14:45",
