        {
            "title": "A股半日跌 深股曾跌近1.3%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日報跌，深股曾跌近1.3%，創業板指數0.94%，兩市成交合計15716.08億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-13.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-13.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日收報4072，跌9點或0.24%，今早以4075點開市，跌6點或0.15%，早段見4080點，跌2點或0.04%，為半日高位，隨即下滑至4062，跌20點或0.48%，為半日低位，隨即窄幅。半日成交6805.96億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日收報14854，跌112點或0.75%，今早開市報14920點，亦跌46點或0.31%。最高報14920，跌46點或0.3%，最低報14920，跌192點或1.28%，為半日低位，半日成交8910.12億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數報4740，跌16點或0.36%，今早開跌6點或0.15%，開報4750點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指數半日報3642，跌34點或0.94%，今早開市報3662點，跌15點或0.42%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15899207-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e6%9b%be%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%911-3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp",
